cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.AI, cs.SI 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper deals with natural language processing and specifically focuses on word discovery in child directed speech. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper presents an unsupervised learning algorithm for word discovery. 
- cs.SD (Sound) is a possible category as the paper deals with speech segmentation, but it is less likely than the previous two categories. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) are also possible categories as the paper deals with modeling and analyzing language data, but they are less likely than the previous categories.
